-keep developing tools for analysis
-try to incorporate generally used analytical tools under the presented framework

>applications and relations to other disciplines and theories
-survey for more concrete applications of the developed framework and instruments
-how does it relates to persistent homology?},
author = {Fischer, Klaus and Schillo, Michael and Siekmann, J{\"{o}}rg},
